circle_yml.string:
version: 2
jobs:
  build:
    docker:
      - image: circleci/node:8
    working_directory: ~/build

    steps:
      - checkout
      - setup_remote_docker
      - run:
          name: Deployment script
          command: |
            export andariel_branch=develop
            if [[ "$CIRCLE_BRANCH" == "master" ]]; then export andariel_branch=master; fi
            curl -f --header "Authorization: token $GIT_TOKEN" https://raw.githubusercontent.com/OpusCapita/andariel/$andariel_branch/buildscript.sh > buildscript.sh
            chmod +x buildscript.sh
            ./buildscript.sh opuscapita/$CIRCLE_PROJECT_REPONAME

  copy_to_env:
    docker:
      - image: circleci/node:8
    working_directory: ~/build

    steps:
      - checkout
      - run:
          name: Mirror Script
          command: |
            export andariel_branch=develop
            if [[ "$CIRCLE_BRANCH" == "master" ]]; then export andariel_branch=master; fi
            curl -f --header "Authorization: token $GIT_TOKEN" https://raw.githubusercontent.com/OpusCapita/andariel/$andariel_branch/mirrorscript.sh > mirrorscript.sh
            chmod +x mirrorscript.sh
            ./mirrorscript.sh opuscapita/$CIRCLE_PROJECT_REPONAME $FROM_ENV $TO_ENV $GIT_TOKEN

  build_base:
    docker:
      - image: circleci/node:8
    working_directory: ~/build

    steps:
      - checkout
      - setup_remote_docker
      - deploy:
          name: Build and push Docker base image
          command: |
            docker build -t opuscapita/$CIRCLE_PROJECT_REPONAME:base -f Dockerfile.base .
            docker login -u $DOCKER_USER -p $DOCKER_PASS
            docker push opuscapita/$CIRCLE_PROJECT_REPONAME:base

circle_yml.string:
version: 2
jobs:
  build:
    docker:
      - image: circleci/node:8
    working_directory: ~/build

    steps:
      - checkout
      - setup_remote_docker
      - run:
          name: Run tests with coverage and post it to coverrals.io
          command: |
            mv .dockerignore .dockerignore_tmp_disabled
            docker-compose -f docker-compose.unit.yml up
            mkdir junit
            docker cp $(docker ps -l -q):/home/node/invoice/test-results.xml ./junit/test-results.xml
            mv .dockerignore_tmp_disabled .dockerignore
            exit $(docker ps -l -q | xargs docker inspect -f '{{ .State.ExitCode }}')
      - store_artifacts:
          path: ./junit/test-results.xml
          prefix: tests
      - store_test_results:
          path: ./junit
      - run:
          name: Deployment script
          command: |
            export andariel_branch=develop
            if [[ "$CIRCLE_BRANCH" == "master" ]]; then export andariel_branch=master; fi

            curl -f --header "Authorization: token $GIT_TOKEN" https://raw.githubusercontent.com/OpusCapita/andariel/$andariel_branch/buildscript.sh > buildscript.sh

circle_yml.string:
machine:
  pre:
   - curl -sSL https://s3.amazonaws.com/circle-downloads/install-circleci-docker.sh | bash -s -- 1.10.0
   - pip install --force-reinstall -U docker-compose==1.10.0
   - sudo pkill -f dnsmasq
   - cd config ; rm -Rf wiki ; git clone https://github.com/OpusCapitaBusinessNetwork/config.wiki.git wiki
  services:
    - docker

dependencies:
  pre:
    - echo -e "$NPM_USERNAME\n$NPM_PASSWORD\n$NPM_EMAIL" | npm login

test:
  override:
    - >
        export HOST_IP=$(ifconfig | grep "docker0" -A1 | grep -o -P "inet addr:.*? " | grep -o -P "\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+") ;
        docker-compose run main npm run test ;
        docker-compose run main npm run test-coverage ;
        docker-compose run main npm run doc
  post:
    - sudo mkdir $CIRCLE_TEST_REPORTS/junit
    - sudo cp test-results.xml $CIRCLE_TEST_REPORTS/junit

deployment:
  npm:
    branch: master
    commands:
      - npm publish
      - npm run upload-coverage
      - cd wiki ; git add --all . ; git commit -am 'Updated documentation.' ; git push ; (exit 0)

all_commit_details.subject: Removed additional logging, set up default secret

circle_yml.string:
version: 2
jobs:
  build:
    docker:
      - image: circleci/node:8
    working_directory: ~/build

    steps:
      - checkout
      - setup_remote_docker
      - run:
          name: Run tests with coverage and post it to coverrals.io
          command: |
            mv .dockerignore .dockerignore_tmp_disabled
            docker-compose -f docker-compose.unit.yml up
            mkdir junit
            docker cp $(docker ps -l -q):/home/node/invoice/test-results.xml ./junit/test-results.xml
            mv .dockerignore_tmp_disabled .dockerignore
            exit $(docker ps -l -q | xargs docker inspect -f '{{ .State.ExitCode }}')
      - store_artifacts:
          path: ./junit/test-results.xml
          prefix: tests
      - store_test_results:
          path: ./junit
      - run:
          name: Deployment script
          command: |
            export andariel_branch=develop
            if [[ "$CIRCLE_BRANCH" == "master" ]]; then export andariel_branch=master; fi

            curl -f --header "Authorization: token $GIT_TOKEN" https://raw.githubusercontent.com/OpusCapita/andariel/$andariel_branch/buildscript.sh > buildscript.sh
            chmod +x buildscript.sh
            ./buildscript.sh opuscapita/$CIRCLE_PROJECT_REPONAME


  copy_to_env:
    docker:
      - image: circleci/node:8
    working_directory: ~/build

    steps:
      - checkout
      - run:
          name: Mirror Script
          command: |
            export andariel_branch=develop
            if [[ "$CIRCLE_BRANCH" == "master" ]]; then export andariel_branch=master; fi
            curl -f --header "Authorization: token $GIT_TOKEN" https://raw.githubusercontent.com/OpusCapita/andariel/$andariel_branch/mirrorscript.sh > mirrorscript.sh
            chmod +x mirrorscript.sh
            ./mirrorscript.sh opuscapita/$CIRCLE_PROJECT_REPONAME $FROM_ENV $TO_ENV $GIT_TOKEN

  build_base:
    docker:
      - image: circleci/node:8
    working_directory: ~/build

    steps:
      - checkout
      - setup_remote_docker
      - deploy:
          name: Build and push Docker base image
          command: |
            docker build -t opuscapita/$CIRCLE_PROJECT_REPONAME:base -f Dockerfile.base .
            docker login -u $DOCKER_USER -p $DOCKER_PASS
            docker push opuscapita/$CIRCLE_PROJECT_REPONAME:base

machine:
  pre:
   - curl -sSL https://s3.amazonaws.com/circle-downloads/install-circleci-docker.sh | bash -s -- 1.10.0
   - pip install --force-reinstall -U docker-compose==1.10.0
   - sudo pkill -f dnsmasq
   - cd config ; rm -Rf wiki ; git clone https://github.com/OpusCapitaBusinessNetwork/config.wiki.git wiki
  services:
    - docker

dependencies:
  pre:
    - echo -e "$NPM_USERNAME\n$NPM_PASSWORD\n$NPM_EMAIL" | npm login

test:
  override:
    - >
        export HOST_IP=$(ifconfig | grep "docker0" -A1 | grep -o -P "inet addr:.*? " | grep -o -P "\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+") ;
        docker-compose run main npm run test ;
        docker-compose run main npm run test-coverage ;
        docker-compose run main npm run doc
  post:
    - sudo mkdir $CIRCLE_TEST_REPORTS/junit
    - sudo cp test-results.xml $CIRCLE_TEST_REPORTS/junit

deployment:
  npm:
    branch: master
    commands:
      - npm publish
      - npm run upload-coverage
      - cd wiki ; git add --all . ; git commit -am 'Updated documentation.' ; git push ; (exit 0)
